{
  "texts": [
    "For enhanced performance, we developed a version that utilizes Tools and Retrieval, FinTralDPO-T&R.",
    "(4) FinTralDPO demonstrates exceptional zero-shot capabilities, outperforming ChatGPT (OpenAI, 2023a) in all tasks.",
    "Moreover, our best model, FinTralDPO-T&R, surpasses GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023b) in five of eight text-based tasks.",
    "The rest of this paper is organized as follows: In Section 2, we review related work with a particular emphasis on financial LLMs, their applications and challenges.",
    "Section 3 outlines how we built our benchmark dataset: FinSet."
  ]
}